DWM

My dwm build, patched with a minimal set of modifications to provide a
more 'sane' starting point for further experiments.

- movemouse, resizemouse and togglefloating taken from dwm-flexipatch
- restartsig
- restoreafterrestart
- viewontag
- viewonrulestag
- savefloats
- floatpos
- resizecorners
- functionality to set initial float geometry

It's essentially what I regard as the bare minimum for my workflow.
